snippet.title: Tricky and the Dream Caster -- SAGE trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the astral plane in my new game, TRICKY AND THE DREAM CASTER!

Take control of Tricky and Volt in this 6th gen inspired platformer as they traverse the realm of dreams in search of the keys to Dream Caster's castle to put an end to a curse placed on Tricky!

Exclusive demo drops on SEPTEMBER 6TH on sagexpo.org and itch.io!
